Question: Explain to a child how to do a task (e.g., cross the street).
Answer:
hi, honey. what kinds of building do you like best? Do you want to see the beatiful building in the opposite of the street? But at first you need to cross the street. The most important thing is pay attention to the traffics in the road. They are very dangerous. When you cross the street, watch the left side first, then watch the right side. Take care of all the cars in the road. Good luck!